songs.title: Move (Acoustic)
songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
(Wo! Hey!)
(Okay)

[Verse 1: Jade]
Hey baby, tell me your name
I got a fever for you
I just can't explain
But there's just one problem
I'm a bit old school
When it comes to loving
I ain't chasing you
Ain't waiting
I'm on a roll
You've got to let yourself go

[Pre-Chorus: Perrie]
(Whoa) You know that I've been waiting for you
(And I noticed you too)
Don't leave me standing all by myself
(I won't leave you standing all alone)
'Cause I ain't looking at no one else
(Oh baby!)

[Chorus: Jesy & All]
Hey, get your back off the wall, don't you get comfortable
Looking so hot, I think that I might fall
Feeling like it's my birthday, like Christmas day came early
Just what I want, so when we move, you move
Hey, get your back off the wall, don't you get comfortable
Looking so hot, I think that I might fall
Feeling like it's my birthday, like Christmas day came early
Just what I want, so when we move, you move

[Verse 2: Leigh-Anne]
Oh silly, why you afraid?
Don't be a big baby, quit playing games
Put your arms around me, you know what to do
And we can take it down low

[Pre-Chorus]
(Whoa) You know that I've been waiting for you
Don't leave me standing all by myself
'Cause I ain't looking at no one else
(Howoa oh oh)

[Chorus: All]
Get your back off the wall (Oh!)
Don't you get comfortable
Looking so hot
I think that I might fall
Feeling like it's my birthday
Like Christmas day came early
Just what I want, so

[Bridge: Leigh-Anne]
I know that you want to
But you can't
Because you got to stay cool in the corner
When the truth is that you want to move
So move

[Pre-Chorus: Perrie]
Move it baby
You know that I've been waiting for you
Don't leave me standing all by myself
'Cause I ain't looking at no one else
Looking at no one else
Looking at no one else (Ow!)

[Bridge: All]
Hey! Hey! I'm ready
Hey! boy come and get me
Don't be scared
Show me what you do
Don't you know a girl like a boy who moves?

[Chorus: All]
Hey, get your back off the wall, don't you get comfortable
Looking so hot, I think that I might fall
Feeling like it's my birthday, like Christmas day came early
Just what I want, so when we move, you move

[Bridge: All]
Hey, hey, I'm ready, hey
Boy come and get me
Don't be scared, show me what you do
Don't you know a girl like a boy who moves
